          This application is secured through
          <span style="color:#233e8b;">OAuth 2.0 Google Email Authentication.</span> <br><br>
          There are various features of this
          application: Searching mechanic services and more services, Storing,
          Accessing and updating data from <a href="https://www.mongodb.com/" style="color:green;">MongoDB</a>.<br><br>
          <b><em>New Horizon</em></b> Web Application provides better user interface so that the
          users can interact with this application conveniently. <br><br>
          For backend
          development, we have used Node.js and it's framework.<br><br>
          For Frontend development, we have
          used HTML, CSS and Bootstrap. <br><br>
          This application is developed in Hyper
          Terminal. We have used Atom as a text editor. Hyper Terminal provides all
          the tools for developing the web application. Hyper Terminal creates user
          computer as a local server. We can run our application through any Web
          Browser. <br><br>
          <span style="color:red;">For Our recommendation open in Chrome Browser.</span>

        </p>
